{"tid":1398521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（發大財）韓國瑜上台後高雄逾千公司執笠","createTime":"2019-08-02T22:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T00:09:30.000Z","uid":41404,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"de5f0710a381026d9945ed345b4be035bdb753f4","tid":1398521,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:43:02.000Z","msg":"聲言「政治0分經濟100分」、要「發大財」的高雄市長韓國瑜，上任後未有理會市政「不務正業」，只顧爭國民黨總統提名，選舉承諾會部走數。台灣經濟部統計，韓國瑜上任逾半年，不但做不到他聲言的「萬商雲集」，反而有1,530間公司倒閉，「跑贏」全台各直轄市。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook群組「高雄好過日」轉載經濟部統計各直轄市公司增城數目的資料，發現包括台北、新北、桃園、台中及台南，公司數目都有所增長，只有高雄的企業數目減少，而且更是「千商倒閉」，批評「市長只拼政治，讓認真拼經濟的市民苦不堪言」，更稱「韓國瑜競選團隊的謊言不攻自破，更可認證韓國瑜一心只有選舉、只想發大財、卻無心市政，害慘高雄的事實」。<br />\n<br />\n群組公佈數字前，民進黨桃園市議員王浩宇早在今年4月已提出警告，指高雄市今年頭3個月登記公司數目減少825間，但其他直轄市卻在增長中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190802/59888939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190802%2F59888939&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDRD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=55219a24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190802%2F59888939&h=c8c51441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190802/59888939</a>"},{"pid":"f49ae5e6d4def9d87f488b365bc6e5756efcad83","tid":1398521,"uid":44454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:47:04.000Z","msg":"清盤公司發大財"},{"pid":"00a954889d8944fb038da9cca451a8d9ded0fb8d","tid":1398521,"uid":75877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f49ae5e6d4def9d87f488b365bc6e5756efcad83","tid":1398521,"uid":44454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:47:04.000Z","msg":"清盤公司發大財"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f53fd692d4b351e4d3388292900b5afdd4ce1c","tid":1398521,"uid":97240,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T22:55:24.000Z","msg":"共產黨既狗係咁上下"},{"pid":"8874f375124e10976d28020dc79dbd289d37f1bb","tid":1398521,"uid":111054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:01:00.000Z","msg":"直轄市當中，高雄係最冇發展潛力既一個<br />\n人口又唔夠台中多"},{"pid":"fad0970907a00ae309ffbc17d602fa50bdf1ab1f","tid":1398521,"uid":47311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:03:00.000Z","msg":"咪啱晒發大財計劃<br />\n做總統全國大執笠，終蟈出手救"},{"pid":"320a497ef851ffec1d790a95c0f49da9905ff8a1","tid":1398521,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8874f375124e10976d28020dc79dbd289d37f1bb","tid":1398521,"uid":111054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:01:00.000Z","msg":"直轄市當中，高雄係最冇發展潛力既一個<br />\n人口又唔夠台中多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:03:22.000Z","msg":"地理位置問題，高雄夏天係好撚熱，返工只可以去留高雄或台中，台北返工除非公司包車錢"},{"pid":"60619ba8c3a40bbd99d333c951c234797b68fcea","tid":1398521,"uid":71997,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:08:36.000Z","msg":"緊係係蔡英文搵食好啦，自己友個個年薪幾百萬，下面嘅，跟蔡總統出國一次買一萬條免稅煙又賺五六百萬，不過今次唔成功啫，但係唔跟佢搵食果啲人就仆街囉，經濟差到無倫，大學生出嚟做嘢先行五六千港紙，死得啦。"},{"pid":"b6223221ba062aabc39f26975ba718f608513cf7","tid":1398521,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"678178b7c9549fa75909efb1b16784f3b6d8d19e","tid":1398521,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60619ba8c3a40bbd99d333c951c234797b68fcea","tid":1398521,"uid":71997,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T23:08:36.000Z","msg":"緊係係蔡英文搵食好啦，自己友個個年薪幾百萬，下面嘅，跟蔡總統出國一次買一萬條免稅煙又賺五六百萬，不過今次唔成功啫，但係唔跟佢搵食果啲人就仆街囉，經濟差到無倫，大學